        {
            "title": "達利歐稱隨著債務增加 美國的貨幣秩序岌岌可危",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 達利歐表示，美國政府債務的累積正在危及貨幣秩序。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「你正看到貨幣秩序受到威脅，」達利歐周五在新加坡舉行的FutureChina Global Forum一個小組討論會上表示。「其他因素將共同決定我們是否會看到整個美國帝國的終結。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位橋水創始人表示，美國超支30%，需要出售 12萬億美元的債務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「全球市場對這類債務沒有同樣的需求，這就造成了供需失衡，」他表示，並將信貸失控歸咎於「人性」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1f989af6-2dd8-3ebc-9600-1f782008a236-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ray Dalio Says US Monetary Order Is at Risk as Debt Mounts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%94%E5%88%A9%E6%AD%90%E7%A8%B1%E9%9A%A8%E8%91%97%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E5%B2%8C%E5%B2%8C%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B1-055631777.html",
